title: Bill Maher gets schooled on vaccines by Bill Frist
description: This was on "Real Time with Bill Maher", 9 October 2009. Maher, who "does not believe" in vaccines, gets a lesson in medicine from former Senate Majority Leader Bill Frist, a heart surgeon.
